column2: SELECT TOP # chinook.Album.ArtistId, chinook.Track.AlbumId, count (*) as NUM_TRACKS, SUM (chinook.Track.UnitPrice) TotalPrice FROM chinook.Track INNER JOIN chinook.Album ON chinook.Track.AlbumId = chinook.Album.AlbumId GROUP BY chinook.Track.AlbumId GROUP BY chinook.Album.ArtistId ORDER BY TotalPrice DESC
